<blockquote><p>Employee earnings have dropped 2% in real terms in the past year and by 8% in the past decade.</p></blockquote>
<p>Here is <a href="https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.economist.com/finance-and-economics/2023/09/28/investors-enthusiasm-for-japanese-stocks-has-gone-overboard" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">more from Buttonwood at The Economist</a>.</p>
